{"tid":1404991,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"比你佔左警署，又如何？","createTime":"2019-08-04T07:08:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T11:27:54.000Z","uid":40720,"like":7,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"54ba04c608e667eb2077ad078110f99ed9ce94ce","tid":1404991,"uid":40720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:08:50.000Z","msg":"依家全港已經進入左亂戰mode<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家不停咁係到諗戰爭嘅佈置，用唔同嘅魔法，佈陣，去對付黑警。<br />\n無錯！我地針對嘅，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係黑警，同埋為我地犧牲左嘅義士。</span></span></strong><br />\n但係不停咁同警抗爭，係咪真係會得到我地想要嘅野？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就算比你佔左警署又如何？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地不如針對返有權力去完結整件事嘅人--- <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭！！！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/04/144950_7e0d406179156cbf59c134f570d74b8d.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F04%2F144950_7e0d406179156cbf59c134f570d74b8d.PNG&h=2dc2c45a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">只要林鄭一聲令下，獨委會就會被成立，警察就開始會被制裁。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家我地不停咁向警斯壓，但係佢地都唔係當權者，就算比你打贏曬，<br />\n黑警敗走，我地佔埋警署，咁又點？   換黎嘅只係更多嘅CCTVB 19 報導，每日警方係記招講返又有幾多人被捕，etc...而當權者---淋病 繼續置身事外，食花生，用警黎做政治盾牌，由得你地續繼打，自己慢慢被淡化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實依家係咪有d wrong focus？係咪更應該一齊整9淋病，多過無了期咁戰爭？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">革命尚未成功，同志仍需努力</span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">加油香港</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e63bce87444bf6be6e8963b12cae06a523a9d4da","tid":1404991,"uid":40720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:08:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cd1aaa0b52adacf7b5cd458da67928c48d94639f","tid":1404991,"uid":40720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:09:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"93a2251770cb930fb8142ad398fd94755bd3cc74","tid":1404991,"uid":40720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:09:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3b1e8e406bb1036d0a5d9caad18bc79bdceba637","tid":1404991,"uid":40720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:09:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7a273ccace8f07522db40a8f474e3701f33d07e7","tid":1404991,"uid":40720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:09:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7d5440600137e0ba5259fdd0ade96bb4ffb80994","tid":1404991,"uid":40720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:10:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d41e13c253f1f22378fe04890a0d9db2e8c855fb","tid":1404991,"uid":40720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:10:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7a41ec251909bdd90977b3909c68a0808a474b2c","tid":1404991,"uid":173326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:12:08.000Z","msg":"警署入面有咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dbbf9e4f048d9f3e6776d3164d868bb7ad0cc5d","tid":1404991,"uid":40720,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"7a41ec251909bdd90977b3909c68a0808a474b2c","tid":1404991,"uid":173326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:12:08.000Z","msg":"警署入面有咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:19:21.000Z","msg":"就算比我地拎到，要講武力，一定贏唔到警。到時佢地可以好合理地用真子彈。而我地有真彈，都合理化地可以出解放軍"},{"pid":"d6f170f39b257bafca376fda6a83babce44e90d0","tid":1404991,"uid":52520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9dbbf9e4f048d9f3e6776d3164d868bb7ad0cc5d","tid":1404991,"uid":40720,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"7a41ec251909bdd90977b3909c68a0808a474b2c","tid":1404991,"uid":173326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:12:08.000Z","msg":"警署入面有咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:19:21.000Z","msg":"就算比我地拎到，要講武力，一定贏唔到警。到時佢地可以好合理地用真子彈。而我地有真彈，都合理化地可以出解放軍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:24:05.000Z","msg":"就係想出老解   怕你唔敢出真子彈同老解咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3e709a1a95f42ab9ca30a7a4c4f36597c6a3ee0","tid":1404991,"uid":48020,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:25:53.000Z","msg":"冇人要佔警署，撚狗炸嘛！"},{"pid":"5c5790bffd287ead1e578ffbbc2dc798c69a57e0","tid":1404991,"uid":64580,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:26:08.000Z","msg":"黑警問題由14年一直存在<br />\n唔覺得有咩目標轉變"},{"pid":"e21d28a9900afeea23886bccef537466e5e0dd8b","tid":1404991,"uid":35815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:26:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a8a3226c0873db6e9d953ddabe54ddbf01cfcc4","tid":1404991,"uid":284317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:27:54.000Z","msg":"邊個話佔左一定要打生打死<br />\n佔到咪名正然順取代黑驚維持治安囉"},{"pid":"0e0e77fbac1a89471925170ff8c81901ddc21034","tid":1404991,"uid":201930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:33:17.000Z","msg":"會唔會攪錯左，已經唔係林鄭攬黑警，係已經去到共匪攬"},{"pid":"953315cad26cabf0b8540ad1f926a7d3018743d1","tid":1404991,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dbbf9e4f048d9f3e6776d3164d868bb7ad0cc5d","tid":1404991,"uid":40720,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"7a41ec251909bdd90977b3909c68a0808a474b2c","tid":1404991,"uid":17