Time":"2019-08-04T07:53:53.000Z","msg":"巴打唔係以為真係林鄭話事呀？習種話事架<br />\n咁你不如直接叫義士對準習種啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你搞掂班黑警，到時你同林鄭玩SM都得啦"},{"pid":"095fe76204467238e950e249bf00d37f288b17dd","tid":1404991,"uid":40720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1c682545ce70ade6cce8268f47c321a0810696fb","tid":1404991,"uid":112583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:51:42.000Z","msg":"獨委會就會被成立=/=警察就開始會被制裁<br />\n<br />\n調查完可以冇事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:54:53.000Z","msg":"唔係一定，但係成立得，就好大可能制裁到<br />\n如果個獨委會會員，都係監警會咁廢，香港人唔會收貨"},{"pid":"59fdef338033ffa2c17b9e28e91a40d7dbc0ce4c","tid":1404991,"uid":40720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bda81c0121ef486364f9777ba9ab771c1514e23a","tid":1404991,"uid":282910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:53:53.000Z","msg":"巴打唔係以為真係林鄭話事呀？習種話事架<br />\n咁你不如直接叫義士對準習種啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你搞掂班黑警，到時你同林鄭玩SM都得啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:56:39.000Z","msg":"我假設，你講ko黑警，係講緊所有警署被佔，但係係你ko黑警前，解放軍已經會出左黎"},{"pid":"66557fd5173e475de81f1e0d51bdbfbfa21737b3","tid":1404991,"uid":284317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59fdef338033ffa2c17b9e28e91a40d7dbc0ce4c","tid":1404991,"uid":40720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bda81c0121ef486364f9777ba9ab771c1514e23a","tid":1404991,"uid":282910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:53:53.000Z","msg":"巴打唔係以為真係林鄭話事呀？習種話事架<br />\n咁你不如直接叫義士對準習種啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你搞掂班黑警，到時你同林鄭玩SM都得啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:56:39.000Z","msg":"我假設，你講ko黑警，係講緊所有警署被佔，但係係你ko黑警前，解放軍已經會出左黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:53:15.000Z","msg":"出得未<br />\n又話8月4出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}